0T15:06:15Z","author_association":"COLLABORATOR","active_lock_reason":null,"body":"Long story short, I made a significant mistake in implementation that affects all configurations. Namely, unpadding and striding along frequency, in freq scattering. My bad.\r\n\r\nGood news is, only `aligned=False` and `'recalibrate'` are severely affected. `aligned=True` and `'resample'` may oversample for non-smallest `N_frs`, and `out_3D=False` may unpad incorrectly. It's possible, and likely, that `True` and `'resample'` work entirely correctly for a given config, just not guaranteed. Implications are \"excess data\" and \"some info lost\", and latter should be negligible in most cases.\r\n\r\nI will fix it, hopefully soon. I'll open it as a PR to #781, write a summary of changes to guide reviewers, and take any questions. For now, `'resample'` and `aligned=True` should work well enough.\r\n\r\n@lostanlen @rastegah @lylyhan @changhongw","closed_by":{"login":"MuawizChaudhary","id":39755015,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjM5NzU1MDE1","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/39755015?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/MuawizChaudhary","html_url":"https://github.com/MuawizChaudhary","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/MuawizChaudhary/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/MuawizChaudhary/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/MuawizChaudhary/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/MuawizChaudhary/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/MuawizChaudhary/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/MuawizChaudhary/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/MuawizChaudhary/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/MuawizChaudhary/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/MuawizChaudhary/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/kymatio/ky